@time=2012-06-17T20:09:18.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :All right, let's get started, then.
@time=2012-06-17T20:10:19.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Things were rather tense last night, what with the specter of an unsolved murder hanging on everyone's minds, but you were able to get a long, if fitful, sleep.
@time=2012-06-17T20:11:01.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Today, you're headed back to Brother Eliezer's place in order to make some headway on finding out who killed Brother Jules, and why.
@time=2012-06-17T20:11:56.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Eliezer is waiting outside of the local officials' post. He looks somewhat weary, but also relieved. Evidently, knowing that the agricultural units will hold out a little longer has eased his worries.
@time=2012-06-17T20:13:59.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Good morning, brothers," he says, waving to you as you approach. "Were you able to rest well? I hope the accommodations were adequate. You likely deserved better, but that's all we had..." **
@time=2012-06-17T20:15:25.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"They were fine," Gideon says, waving off the man's flattery. He isn't pleased with having given Jules' murderer another night to hide, but it couldn't be helped.
@time=2012-06-17T20:15:32.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"We've been sleeping under the stars, Brother Eliezer.  Any accomodation is quite welcome."  Rashi smiles.
@time=2012-06-17T20:16:46.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :14"it couldn't be helped" // Gideon's got some Japanese blood in him, it looks like. ^_~
@time=2012-06-17T20:17:05.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[that expression bugs the hell out of me >_>]
@time=2012-06-17T20:17:19.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(hm?)
@time=2012-06-17T20:18:08.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[nevermind]
@time=2012-06-17T20:19:13.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"That's good to hear," Brother Eliezer says. "I'm going to bring you to talk to our branch Steward, Brother Leslie.
@time=2012-06-17T20:21:10.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"He's not yet been able to get much closer to the truth of Brother Jules' death than any of the rest of us have, but I have faith that the King of Life will illuminate his path."
@time=2012-06-17T20:21:48.000Z :Barcode NICK Barcathon
@time=2012-06-17T20:22:06.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION nods.
@time=2012-06-17T20:22:22.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Eliezer walks into the officials' post, and up some rickety wooden steps to the small second-floor space.
@time=2012-06-17T20:23:10.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie is an older man. The glint of experience reflects from his eyes. He has clearly been Steward for a long time.
@time=2012-06-17T20:23:38.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Thank you, Brother Eliezer," he says, sending the younger man off.
@time=2012-06-17T20:24:34.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Rashi and Gideon take their respective improptu seats on a pair of wooden crates, at the Steward's invitation.
@time=2012-06-17T20:25:13.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I wish we were able to meet under better circumstances, brothers." **
@time=2012-06-17T20:30:06.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION idly prods Rashi and Gideon
@time=2012-06-17T20:30:07.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION glances at Gideon before saying "Likewise, Steward."
@time=2012-06-17T20:30:59.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :14I have this mental image now of Gideon falling asleep until Rashi pokes him in the side.
@time=2012-06-17T20:31:22.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon is momentarily hung up on the fact that his position as a Dog puts him above a Steward, a person who has always been in charge of him until now. After a moment he recovers, "Yes, it's very unfortunate."
@time=2012-06-17T20:31:58.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :14That works too.
@time=2012-06-17T20:33:08.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Was kind of caught on what to say. I want Gideon to be kind of brash and rough with people, but Stewards are kind of supposed to be respected. So yeah.)
@time=2012-06-17T20:33:42.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Brother Eliezer has informed me that the immediate crisis has been resolved. I cannot thank the two of you enough. Particularly you, Brother Rashi. Your skills are a gift to us."
@time=2012-06-17T20:34:53.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie folds his hands. "However, I'm sure the both of you know that this is just the surface. The tensions that lead to hatred and murder are not so easily assuaged.
@time=2012-06-17T20:35:33.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Allow me to be blunt. I take it the two of you have met Brother Joseph?" **
@time=2012-06-17T20:36:07.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Ah, yes, of course." Rashi's pride evaporates.  "Yes, we have... what about him?"
@time=2012-06-17T20:36:08.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"He was quite a disagreeable man," Gideon says.
@time=2012-06-17T20:36:42.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(brb btw)
@time=2012-06-17T20:37:45.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Yes. I hate to condemn a man so readily, but ever since this crisis began, he has been... an agitator is the best way to put it, I believe."
@time=2012-06-17T20:38:28.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie looks out of a nearby window for a moment.
@time=2012-06-17T20:38:50.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Suddenly, a sniper's bullet tears through his brain.)
@time=2012-06-17T20:39:24.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"He's been calling for Brother Eliezer's removal, I suspect in order to take his place. I think his pride has gotten the better of him.
@time=2012-06-17T20:39:58.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"He has two young siblings as well. I suspect they may be easily swayed to his cause. Perhaps they've already been.
@time=2012-06-17T20:41:23.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"And he's always had a bit of a taste for revenge. The Brother Joseph I know wouldn't go so far as to kill a man, but he might be able to instill that desire in others.
@time=2012-06-17T20:42:06.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I've always been a man of words. This may be naive of me, but I'd like the two of you to talk to him and see what comes to light." **
@time=2012-06-17T20:43:09.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"We can talk to him, Brother. I'd like to know some more about the situation first, however. It would be rough to blunder into this feud blindly."
@time=2012-06-17T20:43:30.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[sorry, but can we pause for a few minutes?  I've been putting this off too long...]
@time=2012-06-17T20:43:52.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(I'm fine with that.)
@time=2012-06-17T20:44:11.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Sure. Let's go ahead and break for an intermission.
@time=2012-06-17T20:44:24.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Alright, sorry, I'll try to finish this up AFAP.
@time=2012-06-17T20:45:03.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :AFAP sounds like a very bad sound effect in a doujin.
@time=2012-06-17T20:46:32.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Motoko`kaseijin: You ever played 4th edition DnD?
@time=2012-06-17T20:48:31.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'd never actually done any role-playing before ARE.
@time=2012-06-17T20:48:45.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Ah, I see.
@time=2012-06-17T20:49:15.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :We just introduced a coworker to DnD on Friday. He was a bit confused about the idea of being able to just say what you do. And having a DM.
@time=2012-06-17T20:50:11.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Haha.
@time=2012-06-17T20:50:22.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"What do you mean, there aren't any action buttons?"
@time=2012-06-17T20:50:39.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I can kind of see that, yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T20:51:07.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Well, we played a short encounter with premade characters to get an idea of how the game played. He stole some keys from a guard and then found a chest. Instead of using the keys he spent three turns trying to pick the lock.
@time=2012-06-17T20:51:50.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Maybe he just really wanted to practice lock-picking...
@time=2012-06-17T20:52:41.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Maybe. It was actually a pretty fun little encounter. 4E is kind of weird, but it does make combat less of a hassle.
@time=2012-06-17T20:53:06.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Fewer calculations to make, I take it?
@time=2012-06-17T20:53:12.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Speaking of DnD, I have my setting planned enough to do a trial adventure in a couple weeks, if people are interested.
@time=2012-06-17T20:53:28.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah. And all your skills are on action cards and easy to understand when and how to use them.
@time=2012-06-17T20:53:34.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Solstace: I'd be cool with it.
@time=2012-06-17T20:54:49.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'll probably sit this one out, since I've never been a fan of the D&D style of setting, though I might be persuaded otherwise.
@time=2012-06-17T20:54:55.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, and classes in 4E are divided into archetypes based on how they fight. Very MMO like actually, but that's not a terrible thing when you're just starting into roleplaying.
@time=2012-06-17T20:55:06.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm sure Solstace won't miss the haranguing. >_<
@time=2012-06-17T20:55:25.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Motoko`kaseijin: You should play. We can be a pair of kobolds.
@time=2012-06-17T20:55:38.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Kobold acrobats.
@time=2012-06-17T20:55:40.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, so it makes it easier to understand how the classes are divided?
@time=2012-06-17T20:55:41.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :From a circus.
@time=2012-06-17T20:56:34.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Do our special moves involve throwing opponents into the air and then "barely" failing to catch them on the way down?
@time=2012-06-17T20:56:35.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Motoko`kaseijin: I'm actually trying to avoid the usual kind of DnD setting.  Which is a lot harder than I initially thought XD
@time=2012-06-17T20:56:37.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah. There are strikers, controllers, leaders, and defenders. Strikers do lots of damage. Controllers do crowd control. Leaders buff and debuff. Defenders are tanks.
@time=2012-06-17T20:58:17.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Solstace, yeah, I can imagine. Using the D&D mechanics makes it necessary to have certain aspects no matter what setting you use, I'd guess.
@time=2012-06-17T20:58:34.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Well, you can always use the d20 Modern stuff.
@time=2012-06-17T20:58:42.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Not that I've looked at it ever.
@time=2012-06-17T20:58:44.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :One of the supplements?
@time=2012-06-17T20:58:45.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :But I'm not really using a modern setting.
@time=2012-06-17T20:59:08.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :What kind of setting are you thinking?
@time=2012-06-17T21:00:44.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I've always been a little skittish on mechanics-heavy systems. I think the only reason I made it through ARE is that everyone else was just as new to it. >_>
@time=2012-06-17T21:00:50.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :My vague notion going into this was that I wanted something more JRPGish than DnD.  This further evolved into wanting to get rid of a lot of the random combat, with experience coming more from political encounters, with the occasional faction battle here and there.
@time=2012-06-17T21:00:57.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Happy Gendo Day, everyone!
@time=2012-06-17T21:01:07.000Z :Solstace KICK #madokamadness JBridge :JBridge
