@time=2012-06-17T21:02:13.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I... I just really like kobolds, okay?
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:13.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I made this thread, as you might've guessed.
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:15.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm still considering whether I want to have Elves or not.
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:21.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :tl;dr I'm a newbie GM, need help.
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:30.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :All the other races are out.
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:37.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Solstace: What is this?
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:44.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :back.
@time=2012-06-17T21:02:52.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Just humans? No bishie elves or veira?
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:04.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :If there are elves, they'll be very, very rare.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:16.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, well, I'd be cool with a political JRPG thing.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:21.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :And the humans are probably going to be where the diversity comes from, a la Elder Scroll.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:29.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :We're taking on Shinra Corp?
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:33.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Is there an adorable mascot sidekick race?
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:38.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Kupo.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:46.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Like, if you're character hails from a certain region, he might have more constitution due to climate or something.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:55.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :As opposed to being a Dwarve.
@time=2012-06-17T21:03:59.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :*Dwarf.
@time=2012-06-17T21:04:56.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :This is also the setting I was talking about a while ago where magic is rather tribal/shamanistic, and all magic-users are persecuted/exiled.
@time=2012-06-17T21:05:30.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Dragon Age?
@time=2012-06-17T21:05:39.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I don't know anything about Dragon Age.
@time=2012-06-17T21:05:40.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :get out of here, gamer
@time=2012-06-17T21:05:47.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The tribal idea came from Xam'd.
@time=2012-06-17T21:05:54.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :so, tibetan buddhism
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:12.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm not familiar with tibetan buddhism.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:22.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :it's what xam'd is based on, I think
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:27.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:29.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :not that that matters.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:30.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :That'd make sense.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:31.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:57.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Anyways, I'll spend the next week trying to finalize and compile all the adjustments I'll be making to the system.
@time=2012-06-17T21:06:57.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :so... when are we resuming
@time=2012-06-17T21:07:26.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I was going to let you guys finish talking. I didn't want to just run over your conversation.
@time=2012-06-17T21:07:35.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, you could have told me >.>
@time=2012-06-17T21:07:50.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :What setting is this? Something original?
@time=2012-06-17T21:08:09.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yes.
@time=2012-06-17T21:08:11.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :JBridge, on the other hand, can be bound, gagged, and thrown in a basement somewhere. ^_^
@time=2012-06-17T21:08:11.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :planet eating trees, I think/
@time=2012-06-17T21:08:14.000Z :JBridge PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Ah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:08:15.000Z :Solstace PRIVMSG #madokamadness :^
