@time=2012-06-17T21:09:01.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION pulls Solstace and JBridge out of the room with a vaudeville hook
@time=2012-06-17T21:09:54.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie speaks. "What would you like to know, Brother Gideon?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:09:59.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :**
@time=2012-06-17T21:10:45.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Does Brother Joseph have a history with Brother Eliezer? An old rivalry or something?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:11:42.000Z :cts JOIN #madokamadness
@time=2012-06-17T21:11:48.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Not anything more unusual than being two townspeople, to my knowledge. Brother Joseph is an ambitious fellow. I suspect some jealousy is at work." **
@time=2012-06-17T21:12:04.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :* two fellow townspeople
@time=2012-06-17T21:12:35.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[um, what's eliezer's position, again? >_>]
@time=2012-06-17T21:13:00.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Liaison with the Territorial Authority.)
@time=2012-06-17T21:13:08.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[ah, right]
@time=2012-06-17T21:13:28.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Since the settlements are dependent on the TA's aid, he has to coordinate shipments and such.
@time=2012-06-17T21:13:57.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It's just that with the impending poor harvest, he also got put in control of emergency food distribution.
@time=2012-06-17T21:14:15.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"And you believe that Brother Joseph or one of his brothers killed Brother Jules to get at Eliezer?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:14:18.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :That's solved for now, but there's clearly something personal at work.
@time=2012-06-17T21:15:39.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon: "Not brothers. One is a young girl, in her teens.
@time=2012-06-17T21:16:16.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(How old is Brother Joseph?)
@time=2012-06-17T21:16:24.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"And yes, loath as I am to say it. They may have sought to delegitimize Brother Eliezer in the eyes of the town, by throwing things into further chaos."
@time=2012-06-17T21:17:04.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I was thinking early, maybe mid-twenties. Think... college revolutionary, I guess?
@time=2012-06-17T21:17:31.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"That's quite serious... you really think he'd endanger everybody just for that?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:18:28.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I don't think he was thinking that far ahead. He may have let his own personal dislike for the man cloud his judgment."
@time=2012-06-17T21:20:40.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :** for what it's worth
@time=2012-06-17T21:21:04.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I think we should try talking to Brother Joseph now," Gideon says.
@time=2012-06-17T21:21:58.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie nods and looks at Rashi. "Are you ready as well?" **
@time=2012-06-17T21:22:03.000Z :cts PRIVMSG #madokamadness :y'know what. drat this. killing an endless wave of megas is an exercise in frustration
@time=2012-06-17T21:22:06.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Yes.  Anything else we should know, Steward?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:23:31.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Only that we must have faith that the King shall see us through this, Brother.
@time=2012-06-17T21:23:44.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Let us go, then."
@time=2012-06-17T21:23:47.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"As always."
@time=2012-06-17T21:24:49.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Brother Leslie rises from his seat, when a loud *bang* rings out. Its volume is such that it's impossible to tell where it came from.
@time=2012-06-17T21:25:13.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(I was kidding about the sniper.)
@time=2012-06-17T21:25:28.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :A few screams follow. Brother Leslie looks at Gideon and Rashi, and begins rushing out of the building.
@time=2012-06-17T21:25:41.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION follows!
@time=2012-06-17T21:26:51.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION does the same, realizing that his rifle is still slung on the saddle of his horse.
@time=2012-06-17T21:26:56.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Out in one of the alleys leading off of the central square, an middle-aged man is restraining a young girl, seeming to fit Brother Leslie's description of Joseph's younger sister.
@time=2012-06-17T21:27:50.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :A gun is dropped at her feet. It doesn't look like anyone is injured, but the struggle is still ongoing. Many townspeople have taken cover in nearby buildings or behind objects outside.
@time=2012-06-17T21:28:35.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The man notices the Dogs and Brother Leslie emerging from the officials' post, and jerks his head in a motion as if to suggest "go back inside!" **
@time=2012-06-17T21:29:09.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION hesitates and stops.
@time=2012-06-17T21:29:33.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon continues forward, "What's going on?"
@time=2012-06-17T21:33:36.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The man yells back. His grip on the girl is tenacious, but it may not be enough. "Sister Constance here was headed up to the square with this gun," he says, kicking at the ground. "She didn't look at nobody coming down the street, just striding straight in, eyes at the ground. She's up to no good. You can see it in her!"
@time=2012-06-17T21:34:11.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Sister Constance pays the newcomers no heed, continuing to fight against her restraints, hoping to take advantage of the distraction.
@time=2012-06-17T21:34:19.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :**
@time=2012-06-17T21:35:48.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(I'm ready to call in the conflict mechanics whenever you are.)
@time=2012-06-17T21:35:50.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(So, if I wanted to walk right up to her and lay on hands, would that count as conflict? (Insert joke about laying on hands)) 
@time=2012-06-17T21:36:08.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :You could do that, yes. You'd have to specify some objective, though.
@time=2012-06-17T21:37:12.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon believes she is possessed and intends to cast the demon out.
@time=2012-06-17T21:37:51.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :very straightforward dude
@time=2012-06-17T21:38:07.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon's all about Old Testament style justice.
@time=2012-06-17T21:38:16.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Not a bad guess. Rashi?
@time=2012-06-17T21:38:41.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(You can jump in later if you feel like now's not the best time to enter.)
@time=2012-06-17T21:39:00.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION suspects Gideon may be suffering gunshot wounds in the future.
@time=2012-06-17T21:39:06.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION hangs back nervously.
@time=2012-06-17T21:39:08.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideons suspects.... yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:39:53.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Hehe.
@time=2012-06-17T21:40:02.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, let me put together some figures right quick.
@time=2012-06-17T21:40:07.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Right.
@time=2012-06-17T21:40:15.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :What arena would this start in?
@time=2012-06-17T21:44:22.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Physical, likely.
@time=2012-06-17T21:44:31.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :You're not exactly trading punches yet.
@time=2012-06-17T21:44:35.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:48:51.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, I've put down some details for Sister Constance at the bottom of the character sheet.
@time=2012-06-17T21:49:26.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm going to roll for Body plus Heart and the demonic relationship.
@time=2012-06-17T21:49:39.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Everything look right here?
@time=2012-06-17T21:50:12.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:50:36.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :That's 3d6+5d6+d6=9d6, then.
@time=2012-06-17T21:50:43.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 9d6
@time=2012-06-17T21:50:44.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :2, 1, 2, 5, 2, 1, 3, 6, 1 == 23
@time=2012-06-17T21:50:55.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :1 1 1 2 2 2 3 5 6.
@time=2012-06-17T21:51:13.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'll roll for Body + Heart along with my trait "executor of the King's will" and my Book of Life. Sound good?
@time=2012-06-17T21:51:36.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, and I'll probably call in my devotion to the faith.
@time=2012-06-17T21:51:39.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :You're aiming for an exorcism, right? That looks good to me.
@time=2012-06-17T21:52:19.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :So that's 2d6+5d6+d6+d6+3d6 = 12d6, I think.
@time=2012-06-17T21:52:19.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :So, 2d6+6d6+1d6+3d6+1d6 = 14d6.
@time=2012-06-17T21:52:48.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :heaven or hell!  let's go!
@time=2012-06-17T21:52:48.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, your Heart is 6d6. Okay. You still had an extra d6, though. >_>
@time=2012-06-17T21:52:59.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, 13d6 then?
@time=2012-06-17T21:53:05.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T21:53:08.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 13d6
@time=2012-06-17T21:53:08.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :6, 3, 2, 3, 1, 5, 6, 1, 5, 1, 6, 4, 4 == 47
@time=2012-06-17T21:53:36.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Haha, I can see this one escalating quickly...
@time=2012-06-17T21:54:01.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :1 1 1 2 3 3 4 4 5 5 6 6 6
@time=2012-06-17T21:54:17.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Seems right. Okay, your raise.
@time=2012-06-17T21:54:29.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Raises are 2 dice?
@time=2012-06-17T21:54:32.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I like the "6 6 6" there.
@time=2012-06-17T21:54:35.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah, just two dice.
@time=2012-06-17T21:56:13.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Raise: 5 6. Gideon strides up to Sister Constance and puts his palm to her forehead. With his free hand he pulls his Book of Life from a pocket inside his coat and begins to read.
@time=2012-06-17T21:56:45.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Out loud of course.
@time=2012-06-17T21:56:59.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It'd be silly if he was just calmly perusing the Bible while exorcising a demon.
@time=2012-06-17T21:58:22.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Constance begins screaming as loudly as possible to block the effect of Gideon's words, a high-pitched, unnatural scream. See 5 6, leave 1 1 1 2 2 2 3.
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:17.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Remaining dice for Gideon: 1 1 1 2 3 3 4 4 5 6 6
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:30.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm going to escalate the conflict, since it's clear she has no chance of winning at this rate. Roll Will. I'm also going to bring in the Passion trait, so I get an additional 6d6.
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:41.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :5d6 for you, I believe.
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:50.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 5d6
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:51.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :4, 4, 3, 2, 4 == 17
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:53.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 6d6
@time=2012-06-17T21:59:54.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :2, 6, 1, 1, 4, 5 == 19
@time=2012-06-17T22:00:01.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION flinches from the sound, but sets about clearing out any remaining bystanders
@time=2012-06-17T22:01:39.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Constance knocks the man restraining her to the ground and charges into Gideon, trying to knock the Book from his hand. Raise 2 5, leave 1 1 1 1 1 2 2 2 2 3 6.
@time=2012-06-17T22:05:45.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon stumbles backwards, but keeps hold on the Book. His superior size and training allows him to hold Constance back for the moment. See 3 4, leave 1 1 1 2 2 3 3 4 4 4 4 5 6 6.
@time=2012-06-17T22:08:25.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I am a servant of the King of Life and you will obey me," Gideon says (Invoking the Ancients), sweeping Constance's feet from under her. He kneels beside her, still holding the book in one hand and keeping his palm pressed to her forehead. Raise 5 6, leave 1 1 1 2 2 3 3 4 4 4 4 6.
@time=2012-06-17T22:08:57.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Karate based exorcisms are all the rage)
@time=2012-06-17T22:09:26.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[I think I saw that movie once!]
@time=2012-06-17T22:10:00.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(I like how Rashi fixes a machine and Gideon beats up a girl.)
@time=2012-06-17T22:10:11.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Fuck yeah! Dogs!)
@time=2012-06-17T22:11:08.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Constance hits the ground hard, taking several cuts to the face. See 2 2 2 2 3, leave 1 1 1 1 1 6, fallout 5d6.
@time=2012-06-17T22:11:47.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I'm going to roll 2d6 for her tenacity trait. Down, but not quite out.
@time=2012-06-17T22:11:49.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 2d6
@time=2012-06-17T22:11:50.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :5, 3 == 8
@time=2012-06-17T22:13:09.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Constance takes a swipe directly at Gideon's face, looking to grab onto his hair or at least leave a few marks. Raise 6 3, leave 1 1 1 1 1 5.
@time=2012-06-17T22:14:06.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[What happened to the dude who was restraining her?]
@time=2012-06-17T22:15:03.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It felt unfair to play him as another NPC. He was mostly just there to set the scene.
@time=2012-06-17T22:15:11.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :[alright.]
@time=2012-06-17T22:15:26.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Imagine that she managed to disable him with a well-placed kick between the legs, if you wish.
@time=2012-06-17T22:15:31.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Without thinking Gideon takes his hand from her forehead and catches her wrist. See 6 3, leave 1 1 1 2 2 3 4 4 4 4.
@time=2012-06-17T22:16:49.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Sister, the King of Life will forgive you if you repent. I know this." Raise 4 4, leave 1 1 1 2 2 3 4 4.
@time=2012-06-17T22:18:15.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, I don't think anything good can come from her taking more fallout, so I give.
@time=2012-06-17T22:18:49.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :I kind of expected you to have her pick up the rifle and shoot me.
@time=2012-06-17T22:19:08.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Oh, no, we're not quite there yet.
@time=2012-06-17T22:19:14.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Good to know.
@time=2012-06-17T22:20:17.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The strength drains from Constance's body, and she slumps to the ground, unconscious. The redness seems to lift from her features. She's actually rather fair-looking, discounting the fresh blood of course.
@time=2012-06-17T22:20:55.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Time to roll some fallout...
@time=2012-06-17T22:20:57.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :!roll 5d6
@time=2012-06-17T22:20:58.000Z :GameServ PRIVMSG #madokamadness :3, 3, 2, 5, 1 == 14
@time=2012-06-17T22:21:09.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Do I need to do anything?
@time=2012-06-17T22:21:29.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Okay, not too bad. She'll probably be fine.
@time=2012-06-17T22:21:52.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon, what do you do here? She's been exorcised.
@time=2012-06-17T22:23:43.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon stands up, as if he's suddenly realized that he's kneeling over a bloody, unconscious and fairly attractive girl his own age. He takes a few steps back and looks back at Rashi, "Um, help?" 
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:03.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Hahahahaha.
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:15.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It's his first time. :P
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:17.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION jogs over
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:30.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"You... she was possessed."
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:39.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :ACTION leans down to check vitals.
@time=2012-06-17T22:24:49.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon just nods, stunned.
@time=2012-06-17T22:25:25.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :A few of the townspeople come out from their hiding places and come to look at the scene.
@time=2012-06-17T22:25:38.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"We should take her to the local healer," a woman says.
@time=2012-06-17T22:26:27.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :A man leans in. "Is she going to be all right?" he asks Rashi. **
@time=2012-06-17T22:27:07.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(I like how Rashi is becoming the guy who does all the finesse related stuff. Fix a machine, make sure people aren't dead, so on, so forth.)
@time=2012-06-17T22:27:12.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Yeah, I think she'll be fine.  Someone, help me carry her to the healer."
@time=2012-06-17T22:28:15.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The man takes her arms and hoists Constance over his shoulders, not seeming to care about the blood.
@time=2012-06-17T22:28:40.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Gideon half-steps forward, expecting someone to rush forward to help, and is relieved when someone does.
@time=2012-06-17T22:29:44.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :The woman looks at Constance, then Rashi and Gideon. "She... something in the way she looked didn't seem... human. I'm so glad you could drive... them... out of her."
@time=2012-06-17T22:29:50.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :**
@time=2012-06-17T22:30:43.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"It's part of our duty," Gideon says, attempting to regain control of the situation. "That would be Brother Joseph's sister?"
@time=2012-06-17T22:32:37.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Yes. She's ordinarily... not like that, at all. She always seems so happy, so innocent, but... with that innocence comes vulnerability. *They* must have turned her into... into that."
@time=2012-06-17T22:32:42.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :**
@time=2012-06-17T22:35:30.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"Hm.  We'll see."
@time=2012-06-17T22:35:41.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :14I think I'm going to wrap up after this closing conversation. We should be able to finish this town's episode next week.
@time=2012-06-17T22:36:10.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :"I think we need to talk to her brother," Gideon says, walking towards his horse. He pulls the old rifle from the saddle and slings the strap across his back. "Let's go."
@time=2012-06-17T22:36:16.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :(Cool, whenever.)
@time=2012-06-17T22:36:41.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :All right, we'll pick up next week as you head down to confront Brother Joseph. *suspense chord*
@time=2012-06-17T22:36:46.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Hah.
@time=2012-06-17T22:36:58.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It's been two and a half hours and I kind of need to eat. >_<
