@time=2012-06-17T22:37:06.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Not at all.
@time=2012-06-17T22:37:24.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Cool. Just want to make sure.
@time=2012-06-17T22:37:26.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :It's really saying a lot about your respective characters, I think.
@time=2012-06-17T22:37:29.000Z :Rashi PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Also that's a weird thing to ask after most of last time was Rashi versus agriculture in the fight of the century
@time=2012-06-17T22:37:51.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah, but I just feel like Gideon is always jumping in and talking and Rashi is like, "Um, okay, yeah."
@time=2012-06-17T22:37:59.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Which does work for the whole character thing.
