@time=2012-06-17T22:38:51.000Z :Gideon PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Yeah.
@time=2012-06-17T22:38:53.000Z :Motoko`kaseijin PRIVMSG #madokamadness :Totally not hinting at anything. ^_^
